{"tid":377641,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"吾系甘刀得？","createTime":"2017-08-27T23:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T13:32:59.000Z","uid":120786,"like":132,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a7b0b293bd2bfa72bd6654d0759d49d4dc89d5","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:00:25.000Z","msg":"吾家吾國吾香港<br />\n系你老母亂咁講<br />\n甘苦寒窗十餘載<br />\n刀刃文盲斥悔改"},{"pid":"1674a62d9edf86a8f0e2ae1814a83fc50e66b5a0","tid":377641,"uid":135170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:01:34.000Z","msg":"hi 好耐冇見"},{"pid":"f39fadbf7ebe524530930657ca15f5b5c14af965","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi 好耐冇見</blockquote><br />\n係唔，早晨"},{"pid":"690ca525ce2a7bf3b46ab9dddcf830c90ff6c178","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>hi 好耐冇見</blockquote><br />\n係啊，早晨</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1d8475b36b0a40d1b7bfb67a70e911d616b656e1","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:13:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d2f61119bf8bcfe23fb0f19dbea1e77fadb528e","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:17:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff32ab9992d30560320c70e2f1d8b5b3ef6a4130","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"課堂 28 「噉」「咁」有分別<br />\n<br />\n　　大家可能接受香港傳媒比較多，難以分別「噉」、「咁」到底有何不同。大家先看看以下例子：「噉搞法唔係路喎！」「咁複雜嘅嘢我未諗過。」其實對於前面的例子如果是不懂粵語的人是不知道表達什麼意思，更不用說其分別。有些人認爲兩個字其實一樣，用一個「咁」字代替就可以。而實際上，這兩個字無論從音、義方面都是不同，絕不是同一個字。<br />\n<br />\n噉：廣州音[gam2敢]<br />\n(解)①指示代詞，這樣，那樣。(例)噉就好嘞。[這樣就好了。] || 呢件事大家都噉睇。[這件事大家都那樣看。]②助詞，似的。(例)苦瓜噉面。[像苦瓜似的臉，比喩愁眉苦臉] || 打鑼噉聲。[形容聲音大，像打鑼似的。]③助詞，地。(例)細細聲噉講。[小聲地說。]<br />\n<br />\n咁：廣州音[gam3禁]<br />\n(解)①這麼；那麼。(例)咁多就夠嘞。[這麼多就夠了] || 枝竹竿要咁長先啱用。[竹竿要這麼長才合用。]②多麼。(例)咁靚[多麼漂亮] || 天氣鬼咁熱。[天氣多麼熱。]<br />\n<br />\n注意：其實在七八十年代的香港也是將這兩字區分開來，不知爲何現在香港都不區分這兩個字寫法，或者受娛樂界影響吧，將兩個字都寫成&ldquo;咁&rdquo;。但正規廣州話字一定要區分這兩字的寫法以及讀音。"},{"pid":"6e0095c4bce41741caa06f6f3ed9de845b6ff231","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:25:41.000Z","msg":"樓上文章to 肥絲大隻"},{"pid":"fdc52372b2fc44f32c34ba55f4858097707c9df3","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7291356875976e3d1c7f5fbd9514f9ce829b66f","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28b2efcc1017b36930ca98adbdc2eb07f75fe4f","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0166d049afc680d88600d5aae0a5b0e31d263fa2","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6ba885cf7264c27e2c25a5ce2e3944db422264","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356a0eed88dc6ab99ab2c0ef88349fe49cc63cea","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:52:32.000Z","msg":"12"},{"pid":"d98b901b64a6e6e3f9535fd0f0728487df303cf4","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:55:44.000Z","msg":"13"},{"pid":"29ec7d827bcf5363c9ee82b660b2577cfdafc970","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as