一火燭死左點算<br />\nb：咁你又住邊呀<br />\na：我住寶林<br />\nb：恕我大鄉里，即係邊度<br />\na：咪係係將軍澳囉，得閒你過一過黎啦</blockquote><br />\n除左個個之外都可以接受</blockquote><br />\nb：點？我路痴唔識行<br />\na：哦，你行錯左左邊，行返轉頭啦"},{"pid":"0ccf513f6431de28c8ea9fa714b8520b66e651f8","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569fcf4b43aae348246fb6ccfde22dcf9f6a4f95","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea76219115cafde3b5db802ffc50017be19c865","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6b48bdc39e1d302b11bca8da25547804113ae3","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b5f00c391c66839f41df0b33d28f258b547883","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cec0ed4b71cdda1727840bbc689783b06f3cc0","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fdeb1ee602cd878fda30fd059e26362accdf85","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd40898d912e36319e65e220bd8dac4f51d8b95","tid":377641,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif